                    <span>Very good book. The content is very precise and has content which will be useful to newbie as a well as to a seasoned MySQL user. I recomment it to all.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Very clear! Best book I found on MySQL</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
